RAD_LOVS.LOV_QUERY: SELECT a.contract_ref_no,a.product_code, a.user_ref_no, a.product_type, a.counterparty, e.product_description, f.customer_name1,'Tranche' Prodtyp, a.contract_ccy FROM oltbs_contract a, OLTMS_PRODUCT e,oltms_customer f WHERE a.module_code = 'LB' AND a.product_type = 'C' AND a.branch = global.current_branch AND a.product_code=e.product_code and a.counterparty=f.customer_no and EXISTS (SELECT 1 FROM smvws_user_branches b, oltb_contract d WHERE b.User_id = Global.user_id AND b.Branch_code = d.Branch)
